 6.805728927720437e-11, \"text\": \"U22\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_under-23_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_national_under-23_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her bout\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 823}, {\"ngram\": \"the 28-year-old Tullamore woman\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 862}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"the five judges' scorecards\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 944}, {\"ngram\": \"Stefanie Von Berge\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There appeared to be very little separating the two boxers in the opening round, so when four of the judges scored it in favour of Von Berge, Walsh's Olympic hopes were in serious jeopardy.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the two boxers\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening round\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1137}, {\"ngram\": \"favour\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"Von Berge\", \"from\": 1161, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"Walsh's Olympic hopes\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1193}, {\"ngram\": \"serious jeopardy\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A brilliant second round from the Offaly woman, in which she took the fight to Von Berge and rattled off some excellent combination punches, put her back in contention on the judges' cards.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Offaly_GAA\", \"score\": 0.9999999999952252, \"rank\": 4.760354199815198e-12, \"text\": \"Offaly\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Offaly_GAA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Offaly_GAA\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A brilliant second round\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngr